column5: New rules coming . No Hunting Seals sold after 11/19 for rest of 2018. Called and C.O. looking to see what can be done for non residents.
Simple.....buy it before the cut off date.
Yup I will just drive up to buy it, o wait 1300 miles round trip before I come up to hunt in dec. Would be nice if you could do it on line or phone.
MNR is working on options for the lic that need game seal. Gord is right you can buy some lic on line but right now not the ones that need a game seal.
